high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left before reaching the couch, go forward to the dresser.
Take the watch between the remote controls from the dresser.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward, turn left to the coffee table.
Put the watch on the coffee table to the right of the book.
Go forward to the coffee table, turn left, go forward and to the right back to the dresser.
Take the watch from the dresser.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward, turn left to the coffee table.
Put the watch between the book and the first watch on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put two watches on a coffee table.

high_descs: Walk around the cabinet to the wooden drawers against the other wall.
Pick up the watch from between the two remotes.
Walk over to the coffee table.
Place the watch down on the coffee table in front of the lap top.
Walk back over to the wooden drawers.
Pick up the watch to the right of the book.
Walk back over to the coffee table.
Put the watch down on the coffee table to the left of the first watch.
anns.task_desc: To move two watches to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right to move around the coffee table to the dresser at the far wall
Pick up the watch from the middle of dresser
Turn around and move to the coffee table
Put the watch by the book on the coffee table
Move back to the dresser on the far wall
Pick up the watch from the left side of the dresser
Turn around and move back to the coffee table
Put the watch on the left side of the other watch
anns.task_desc: Retrieve two watches from the dresser and put the watches on the coffee table.
